title: Selena Gomez's Super Bowl 2017 Instagram Stories - Selena Gomez Stag at Super Bowl Couples' Party
text:
By Alyssa Bailey Feb 5, 2017 Selena Gomez is currently watching the Super Bowl with a bunch of couples. Her new boyfriend The Weeknd doesn't appear to be there, so Gomez is documenting her night as a seventh wheel on her Instagram story the way we all would. A photo posted by Selena & Justin Updates™ (@jelenasenergy) on Feb 5, 2017 at 4:56pm PST Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Perhaps it's her way of sending The Weeknd a "where are you?" shoutout: [Video]: Selena via her Instagram Story.
